\section{Nash bargaining solution}
\label{sec:NashBargainingSolution}

Due to the inefficiency of the NE, a Pareto-efficient solution can be achieved by introducing the cooperation between the players. The resulting solution is called NB solution whose determination requires two elements \cite{Abidi2007}:
